===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|鼠|穴|ls=ic|t1=mouse|t2=hole}} – to hide in a hole.

===Etymology===
Related to {{och-l|鑽|to bore, perforate}}, with semantic shift "to bore" > "to hide (in a bored-out area)" > "to go into exile" (STEDT).

